OL,3,CTax reforms key to solving Guernsey's
OL,4,Cfinancial woes
OL,6,FTax reforms and infrastructure
OL,7,Finvestment in Guernsey are key to
OL,8,Ftackling the island's financial woes,
OL,9,Feconomic advisors have urged.
OL,11,FIt comes as a report from the
OL,12,FIndependent Fiscal Policy Panel
OL,13,Freviewed the States of Guernsey's
OL,14,Frecent spending decisions.
OL,16,FThe experts warned that if the island
OL,17,Fcontinues spending at the current
OL,18,Frate, capital reserves will be
OL,19,Fexhausted by 2032.
