OL,3,CTax reforms key to solving Guernsey's
OL,4,Cfinancial woes
OL,6,FThey found that tax reforms could be
OL,7,Fan important step towards long-term
OL,8,Ffiscal sustainability.
OL,10,FWhile the States have agreed to this
OL,11,Fin principle, no reforms have yet been
OL,12,Fbrought in.
OL,14,FEconomic experts also recommended
OL,15,FGuernsey's government spends at least
OL,16,F3% of its income on infrastructure
OL,17,Fprojects - around #100 million - if
OL,18,Fthey want the Bailiwick to thrive.
