OL,3,CTax reforms key to solving Guernsey's
OL,4,Cfinancial woes
OL,6,FHowever, the States Assembly are
OL,7,Fcurrently struggling to agree to set
OL,8,Faside 2%.
OL,10,FGuernsey is far below other OECD
OL,11,Fcountries such as the UK and Costa
OL,12,FRica when it comes to government
OL,13,Fspending - using only 23% of its GDP.
OL,15,FProfessor Matthew Agawala, the panel's
OL,16,Fchair, says this may also be why
OL,17,FGuernsey is falling behind in many
OL,18,Fleague tables when compared to other
OL,19,Fsmall island economies.
