OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F383A1741953739
OL,3,CTax reforms key to solving Guernsey's
OL,4,Cfinancial woes
OL,6,FHe explains: "Guernsey invests less as
OL,7,Fa share of its GDP in infrastructure
OL,8,Fthan Jersey or other comparable
OL,9,Fjurisdictions and its fiscal position
OL,10,Fis deteriorating fairly quickly.
OL,12,F"There is good news for Guernsey in
OL,13,Fthat it is a wealthy economy, but the
OL,14,Fflip side is that wealthy economies
OL,15,Ftend to grow quite slowly which means
OL,16,Fthey have to run fiscal surpluses to
OL,17,Favoid getting into trouble.
OL,26,@tD@AOU
