OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F383A1741953739
OL,3,CTax reforms key to solving Guernsey's
OL,4,Cfinancial woes
OL,6,F"The challenge is that tax revenues,
OL,7,Fspending, capital infrastructure
OL,8,Finvestment and maintenance of the
OL,9,Freserves have all been on a downward
OL,10,Ftrajectory.
OL,12,F"It is increasingly urgent that these
OL,13,Fthings are all balanced to deliver a
OL,14,Fsustainable future for the economy."
OL,16,FPanel member Matthew Bell says the
OL,17,Fisland needs to commit to spending on
OL,18,Fbig infrastructure projects such as
OL,19,Fhousing, schools, and hospitals to
OL,20,Fbenefit residents.
