OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F383A1741953739
OL,3,CTax reforms key to solving Guernsey's
OL,4,Cfinancial woes
OL,6,FHe adds: "Every project will have a
OL,7,Fset of costs and benefits and it's
OL,8,Fvery important to understand clearly
OL,9,Fwhich are the projects where the
OL,10,Fbenefits clearly outweigh the costs.
OL,12,F"Yes we have to pay for them upfront,
OL,13,Fbut the decision is based on the
OL,14,Fbenefits that are going to serve us
OL,15,Fwell for decades to come."
OL,17,FDeputy Lyndon Trott, President of
OL,18,FGuernsey's Policy & Resources
OL,19,FCommittee, says the panel's findings
OL,20,Fare not surprising.
