OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F383A1741953739
OL,3,CTax reforms key to solving Guernsey's
OL,4,Cfinancial woes
OL,6,FHe explains: "As we stated
OL,7,Fconsistently in the lead-up to the
OL,8,Fdebate on our 2025 Budget proposals,
OL,9,Fthe States has for many years under-
OL,10,Finvested in capital infrastructure and
OL,11,Four proposals focused on that need -
OL,12,Fit's why we called it a budget for
OL,13,Finfrastructure.
OL,15,F"The Assembly agreed on tax reforms
OL,16,Fthat will help address that in the
OL,17,Flong term, but we need to generate
OL,18,Fsurpluses in order to fund much-needed
OL,19,Finfrastructure projects and we simply
OL,20,Fwon't have them in the short term.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G7/8
