OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F383A1741953739
OL,3,CTax reforms key to solving Guernsey's
OL,4,Cfinancial woes
OL,6,F"It means the States' reserves are
OL,7,Fbeing used to fund capital investment
OL,8,Fand to cover the deficits, meaning our
OL,9,Fisland's savings are reducing.
OL,11,F"I am grateful to the independent
OL,12,Fpanel for their work and hope it is of
OL,13,Fuse to the next States."
